    <div class="card-subtle rounded-lg">
      <div class="flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6">
        <h1 class="text-3xl leading-none font-medium">Colin Ding - Academic Resume</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 pt-0">
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-base mb-3">
          Student researcher and competitor at Bergen County Academies, passionate about science, 
          mathematics, and computer science. Experienced in leading teams, conducting research, 
          and mentoring students across multiple disciplines.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <Link href="mailto:colinding10@gmail.com" class="text-foreground inline-flex items-center gap-x-1.5" underline external>
            <Icon name="lucide:mail" class="size-4" />
            colinding10@gmail.com
          </Link>
          <Link href="tel:+12013109504" class="text-foreground inline-flex items-center gap-x-1.5" underline external>
            <Icon name="lucide:phone" class="size-4" />
            (201) 310-9504
          </Link>
          <Link href="https://linkedin.com/in/colin-ding-4b7147305" class="text-foreground inline-flex items-center gap-x-1.5" underline external>
